snippet.title: The Betweenlands Mod - Official Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Introducing The Betweenlands... a dark and hostile environment!

The Betweenlands is a mod for the sandbox construction game, Minecraft developed by the Angry Pixel modding group. This large and expansive mod focuses on a whole new fully fleshed-out dimension for Minecraft with a plethora of exciting new content.

Forum thread - 
http://bit.ly/1RohUnS

Twitter - 
http://bit.ly/1pKGn0y

Wiki - 
http://bit.ly/22Jagfw

The music in this trailer was created specifically for this project by Danny Harrington of Harrowed Creations™.  His website can be found here - 
http://bit.ly/1MG5Wo5
